  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What lies beyond The 4th Wall?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>STORY</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A mind-bending journey into a surreal world. This immersive experience subverts reality through minimalistic visuals and an unsettling landscape, designed to tap into primal fears and curiosities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>GAMEPLAY</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The 4th Wall is a short (approximately 20 minute) experimental visual puzzle / exploration game. Contains little text / dialog, most clues are visual based. You must intuit what to do based on your surroundings and interaction with the world. Not everything is as it seems, so you must pay close attention to move forward. Uses standard FPS controls. Headphones recommended when playing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>NOTES</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Remake of the hit 2012 GZ Storm game of the same name.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Achievements.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgraded visuals.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>GENRE</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Surreal Horror Experimental 3D</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What lies beyond The 4th Wall?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>STORY</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A mind-bending journey into a surreal world. This immersive experience subverts reality through minimalistic visuals and an unsettling landscape, designed to tap into primal fears and curiosities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>GAMEPLAY</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The 4th Wall is a short (approximately 20 minute) experimental visual puzzle / exploration game. Contains little text / dialog, most clues are visual based. You must intuit what to do based on your surroundings and interaction with the world. Not everything is as it seems, so you must pay close attention to move forward. Uses standard FPS controls. Headphones recommended when playing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>NOTES</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Remake of the hit 2012 GZ Storm game of the same name.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Achievements.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgraded visuals.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>GENRE</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Surreal Horror Experimental 3D</p>",
